{"tid":1641354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到咁多人支持梁天琦 但忘記了教主","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T15:49:28.000Z","uid":36995,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58be3ba99b861cbc017196426f07b1baea734734","tid":1641354,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:11:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h0NQy_sobpk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh0NQy_sobpk&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=87f8efa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h0NQy_sobpk</a><br />\n2016年旺角案後<br />\n全立法會都同梁天琦割席<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>民主黨發聲明：回應旺角發生的暴亂，認為事件不能讓兩派容忍、並譴責任何暴力和縱火行為；對於有記者採訪期間遇襲受傷，深表憤怒，譴責襲擊前線警員的暴力行為，對受傷人士致以慰問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>公民黨：譴責暴力行為，指示威者縱火、掟磚、襲擊警員和記者，多人受傷，財物損毀。記者正常採訪受阻、受襲，工作器材被惡性損壞，嚴重破壞新聞自由，公民黨絕對不能接受。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n新民主同盟2月9日發表聲明對旺角衝突事件表示遺憾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n民殘聯等垃圾我就唔貼出黎<br />\n無割席既得學民思潮 青年新政<br />\n<br />\n全立法會唯一得教主依舊支持年輕人<br />\n為梁天琦等義士係旺角衝突事件辯論<br />\n<br />\n教主係連登成人被抹黑<br />\n希望此post可以以正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0439224e72e0e6718a94b2d774365f23991f0a","tid":1641354,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"【行動核彈】隊㝝WeChat妙法！借警察報料熱線一齊將騰訊列美國制裁名單！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情請閱：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641145</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chrsTee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchrsTee.jpg&h=60437086&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b60f04c0ec76cad90ef15de0cfa1349b54ea504b","tid":1641354,"uid":8577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:13:42.000Z","msg":"咁多飯民打手搵食，教主點會唔俾狗咬<br />\n不過唔使為呢啲嘢嘈，明嘅人自然會明，教主咁多年嚟從冇出賣過香港人"},{"pid":"9e8e8bb686ebddbce427f5d93d3e0d6a8db3b977","tid":1641354,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b60f04c0ec76cad90ef15de0cfa1349b54ea504b","tid":1641354,"uid":8577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:13:42.000Z","msg":"咁多飯民打手搵食，教主點會唔俾狗咬<br />\n不過唔使為呢啲嘢嘈，明嘅人自然會明，教主咁多年嚟從冇出賣過香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:20:37.000Z","msg":"所以我咁多年都係教主既粉絲<br />\n因為教主一直都無講過半句有關年輕人既壞話"},{"pid":"5d359adcfc2e88cee18f7df3edc793f989c21c5f","tid":1641354,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}